---
title: Spice-Rubbed Half Chicken with Roasted Figs, Caramelized Onion, and Green Beans
description: Floral honey and salty chicken stock balance each other out to create a sweet yet savory sauce over cinnamon and coriander-rubbed chicken. Fresh figs are transformed into a soft, jammy side after a quick roast in the oven. They’re perfect alongside crisp-tender green beans and roasted onions.
